* [[政委|政委]]：阮文相（{{lang|vi|Nguyễn Văn Tương}}）少將<ref>"加强对海洋、岛屿与海警宣传"[http://cn.news.gov.vn/Home/加强对海洋岛屿与海警宣传/20125/7147.vgp] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120801100354/http://cn.news.gov.vn/Home/%e5%8a%a0%e5%bc%ba%e5%af%b9%e6%b5%b7%e6%b4%8b%e5%b2%9b%e5%b1%bf%e4%b8%8e%e6%b5%b7%e8%ad%a6%e5%ae%a3%e4%bc%a0/20125/7147.vgp |date=2012-08-01 }},越南社会主义共和国中央政府门户网站,9:06-2012/05/05.</ref>

